Genome-wide association studies and cross-population meta-analyses investigating 
short and long sleep duration.

Austin-Zimmerman I(1)(2), Levey DF(3)(4), Giannakopoulou O(1)(5), Deak JD(3)(4), 
Galimberti M(3)(4), Adhikari K(3)(4), Zhou H(3)(4), Denaxas S(6), Irizar 
