Safety and Efficacy of Long-Term Deutetrabenazine Use in Children and 
Adolescents with Tics Associated with Tourette Syndrome: An Open-Label Extension 
Study.

Jankovic J(1), Coffey B(2), Claassen DO(3), Jimenez-Shahed J(4), Gertz BJ(5), 
Garofalo EA(5), Stamler DA(6), Wieman M(7), Savola JM(8), Harary E(9), Alexander 
