Cost-utility analysis of dual-antibiotic cement versus single-antibiotic cement 
for the treatment of displaced intracapsular hip fractures in older adults.

Png ME(1), Costa M(2), Nickil A(3), Achten J(2), Peckham N(4), Reed MR(3); 
WHiTE-8 Investigators.

Collaborators: McAndrew A, Patil S, Dunbar M, Engelke D, Maqsood M, Tsitskaris 
K, Joachim T, Gandhe AJ, Mahmood A, Hawkins R, Rogers B, Bhatnagar S, 
